        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <actionDate>2015-07-30</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Local Zoning Decisions Protection Act of 2015</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of federal funds to:</p> <ul> <li> implement, administer, or enforce the final rule of the Department of Housing and Urban Development entitled &quot;Affirmatively Furthering Fair Housing&quot; (80 Fed. Reg. 42272 [July 16, 2015]); or</li> <li> design, build, maintain, utilize, or provide access to a federal database of geospatial information on community racial disparities or disparities in access to affordable housing. </li></ul>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-10-19T20:57:34Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <updateDate>2015-07-30T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
        </item>
